snippet.title: AIMTROPOLIS TRAILER 1 (official)
snippet.description:
The time has come... we present you the first trailer of AIMTROPOLIS. Our first VR game, an arcade/shooter with 50 minigames. 

You can support us in our Kickstarter! Stay tuned for next week ^^
